{"tid":2019510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府應該豁免從泰國回港市民須隔離的規定","createTime":"2020-05-16T10:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T10:47:41.000Z","uid":166360,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5848124addeae4d07373a4bbd49fda9e5c99162e","tid":2019510,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"泰國將中國大陸、港澳及南韓剔出危險傳染病地區名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526521-20200516.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526521-20200516.htm&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=009a6467\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526521-20200516.htm&h=f7efc1e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526521-20200516.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;由今日開始，將中國大陸、香港、澳門及南韓，剔除出危險傳染病地區的名單。&quot;<br />\n即是從香港入境泰國不會有任何限制措施<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要香港政府豁免從泰國回港市民須隔離的規定，香港市民便能如常去泰國旅遊，亦能扶持香港旅遊界，締造雙贏局面。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2481c846139785d0fa49f3dc7b47a442c96797a7","tid":2019510,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"就算返嚟唔駛隔離，航班之前 cut 咗好多未恢復正常，點去喎"},{"pid":"2264c32f88d7313161a5891a193046723969af2c","tid":2019510,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2481c846139785d0fa49f3dc7b47a442c96797a7","tid":2019510,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"就算返嚟唔駛隔離，航班之前 cut 咗好多未恢復正常，點去喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:41:01.000Z","msg":"香港政府應呼籲航空公司大幅增加來往泰國的航班<br />\n相信到時對機位的需求亦能支持航班的大幅增加"},{"pid":"66bbba0fd4b8ce30a5b1d56a2ed8d9ea2867e277","ti